OL,3,CFamily call for better mental health
OL,4,Cfunding after dad jailed for mum's
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FThe family of a man who beat his wife
OL,8,Fto death with a hammer have called for
OL,9,F"improvements and better funding in
OL,10,Fmental health services across Northern
OL,11,FIreland".
OL,13,FIt comes as former BBC security guard
OL,14,FGary Alexander Baird was today
OL,15,F(Wednesday) handed a seven-year
OL,16,Fsentence after he pleaded guilty to a
OL,17,Fcharge of the manslaughter of his wife
OL,18,FSusan Baird on the grounds of
OL,19,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
