OL,7,FHis sentence included three years jail
OL,8,Fwith four years to be served on
OL,9,Flicence.
OL,11,FGiven the time the 65-year-old served
OL,12,Fwhile awaiting trial, he is to be
OL,13,Freleased later this year.
OL,15,FThe 60-year-old mother-of-four died
OL,16,Ffrom catastrophic head injures in the
OL,17,Fcouple's Windermere Road home in the
OL,18,FFour Winds area of Belfast on the
OL,19,Fafternoon of Sunday August 16, 2020.
