OL,7,FSpeaking after the sentence was
OL,8,Fimposed, the couple's children issued
OL,9,Fa statement which said: "As the four
OL,10,Fchildren of Susan Baird, we welcome
OL,11,Fand accept the verdict of manslaughter
OL,12,Fwith diminished responsibility.
OL,14,F"Through our immense heartbreak, we
OL,15,Fhope to see improvements and better
OL,16,Ffunding in mental health services
OL,17,Facross Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
