OL,7,F"This will never get any easier to say
OL,8,Ffrom me. I struggle to write it, never
OL,9,Fmind say it aloud and I still find it
OL,10,Fextremely hard to believe this is our
OL,11,Freality."
OL,13,FAt the time of her death, Mrs Baird
OL,14,Fworked as an administrator at
OL,15,FOrangefield Presbyterian Church. On
OL,16,Fthe afternoon of her death, she had
OL,17,Fspend some time working from home
OL,18,Funtil around 2.30pm.
