OL,4,Cfunding after dad jailed for mum's
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FAt 4.51pm, Baird called 999 and during
OL,8,Fthe 11-minute phonecall, he admitted
OL,9,Fhe had killed his wife.
OL,11,FDuring the call, Baird said: "I've
OL,12,Fjust murdered my wife."
OL,14,FHe told the operator he had hit her
OL,15,Fwith a hammer and when asked if she
OL,16,Fwas dead, Baird replied "I think so".
OL,18,FPolice and paramedics attended the
OL,19,Fcouple's home where they observed a
OL,20,Fheavily-bloodstained Baird sitting in
OL,21,Fthe kitchen with a wound to his head.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
