OL,7,FThey then discovered Mrs Baird who was
OL,8,Flying slumped on a sofa in a small
OL,9,Froom off the kitchen. She was
OL,10,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,12,FShe sustained catastrophic wounds to
OL,13,Fher head whilst her husband - who was
OL,14,Fbleeding from self-inflicted injuries
OL,15,Fto his head - was agitated and
OL,16,Fconfused at the scene.
OL,18,FAlso present was the hammer Baird used
OL,19,Fin the fatal attack.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
