OL,7,FFollowing his arrest, Baird admitted
OL,8,Fattacking his wife with a hammer and
OL,9,Fsaid 'the voices in my head told me to
OL,10,Fdo it'.
OL,12,FTen days before killing his wife,
OL,13,FBaird jumped in front of a bin lorry
OL,14,Fas it drove down Bedford Street in
OL,15,FBelfast which resulted in him being
OL,16,Fhospitalised.
