OL,7,FThe court heard that whilst there had
OL,8,Fbeen problems within the Baird's
OL,9,Fmarriage, there was no history of
OL,10,Fdomestic violence and that Mrs Baird
OL,11,Fhas been concerned about the decline
OL,12,Fin her husband's mental health.
OL,14,FShe has also expressed fears about his
OL,15,Fmental state after he was released
OL,16,Ffrom hospital following the incident
OL,17,Finvolving the bin lorry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
