OL,7,FThis, Mr McFarland said, could have
OL,8,Fbeen an accident but may well have
OL,9,Fbeen an act of self-harm or an attempt
OL,10,Fat suicide.
OL,12,FIt also emerged that prior to the
OL,13,Ffatal hammer attack, over 570 calls
OL,14,Fhad been made to Baird's GP's practice
OL,15,Fin a bid to seek help - none of which
OL,16,Fwere answered.
OL,18,FAfter he was arrested in the aftermath
OL,19,Fof his wife's death, Baird was
OL,20,Fsectioned and spent a period of time
OL,21,Fdetained under the Mental Health Act.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
