OL,7,FHe was then moved to prison and
OL,8,Fsubsequently pleaded guilty to a
OL,9,Fcharge of manslaughter which was not
OL,10,Faccepted by the Crown.
OL,12,FBaird stood trial earlier this year on
OL,13,Fa charge of murdering his wife.
OL,15,FThe trial commenced in January in
OL,16,Ffront of a jury who heard five days of
OL,17,Fevidence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
