OL,7,FHowever, as the murder trial was due
OL,8,Fto enter its second week, a legal
OL,9,Fissue arose which was dealt with in
OL,10,Fthe absence of the jury.
OL,12,FAfter making a ruling on the legal
OL,13,Fissue, trial judge Mr Justice
OL,14,FMcFarland determined that the jury
OL,15,Fshould be discharged.
OL,17,FThe case was listed again in May and
OL,18,Fon that occasion, Baird pleaded again
OL,19,Fguilty to a charge of the manslaughter
OL,20,Fof his wife Susan Baird by way of
OL,21,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
