OL,10,Fthe conclusion of the case.
OL,12,FAlso reacting to today's sentencing
OL,13,Fwas Detective Inspector Jennifer Rea
OL,14,Ffrom the PSNI who said: "The
OL,15,Finvestigation began with the defendant
OL,16,Freporting his actions to police.
